TITLE: Basic Resource Configuration in Nomad Job
DESCRIPTION: Example showing basic resource configuration with CPU, memory and device requirements in a Nomad job specification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/resources.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
job "docs" {
  group "example" {
    task "server" {
      resources {
        cpu    = 100
        memory = 256

        device "nvidia/gpu" {
          count = 2
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

