TITLE: Running nomad job run command
DESCRIPTION: Basic usage of the 'nomad job run' command to submit a job file to Nomad for scheduling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/commands/job/run.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
nomad job run [options] <job file>
```

