TITLE: Setting Up gRPC Health Checks in Nomad
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for gRPC health checks specifying service, TLS usage, and verification options. The check will verify the 'example.Service' on the 'rpc' port with TLS enabled but certificate verification skipped.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/check.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
service {
  check {
    type            = "grpc"
    port            = "rpc"
    interval        = "5s"
    timeout         = "2s"
    grpc_service    = "example.Service"
    grpc_use_tls    = true
    tls_skip_verify = true
  }
}
```

