TITLE: Basic Environment Variable Configuration in Nomad
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates basic setup of environment variables within a Nomad job specification using the env block.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/env.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
job "docs" {
  group "example" {
    task "server" {
      env {
        my_key = "my-value"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

