TITLE: Inspecting Consul Service Workload Identity Claims in JSON
DESCRIPTION: Example of the claims included in a Nomad workload identity JWT for Consul services. The claims include the service name instead of the task name.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/concepts/workload-identity.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "nomad_namespace": "default",
  "nomad_job_id": "example",
  "nomad_allocation_id": "8623ac7a-28ba-20c3-24a6-e615a39bbbf3",
  "nomad_service": "example-cache-redis"
}
```

