TITLE: Downloading a File Artifact in Nomad
DESCRIPTION: A simple example showing how to download a file from a URL into the task's local directory. The 'local/' path is relative to the task's working directory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/artifact.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
artifact {
  source = "https://example.com/file.txt"
}
```

