TITLE: Accessing Vault KV API v1 Secrets in Nomad Templates (HCL)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to retrieve secrets from Vault's KV API v1 store, including handling secrets with hyphenated names that require index-based access.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/template.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: hcl
