TITLE: Starting Nomad Development Agent
DESCRIPTION: Command to start the Nomad agent in development mode after binary installation. This mode is suitable for testing and development purposes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/install/quickstart.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
sudo nomad agent -dev
```

