TITLE: Configuring Custom Scheduler with HCL in Nomad Server Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Example of configuring a Nomad server with a custom scheduler configuration during bootstrap. This sets up spread scheduling and enables preemption for all job-type schedulers. This configuration is only applied during initial bootstrap.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/configuration/server.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
server {
  default_scheduler_config {
    scheduler_algorithm             = "spread"
    memory_oversubscription_enabled = true
    reject_job_registration         = false
    pause_eval_broker               = false

    preemption_config {
      batch_scheduler_enabled    = true
      system_scheduler_enabled   = true
      service_scheduler_enabled  = true
      sysbatch_scheduler_enabled = true
    }
  }
}
```

