TITLE: Configuring ACL Policy for Variables in HCL
DESCRIPTION: This HCL snippet defines an ACL policy for variables in the 'dev' namespace. It grants full access to variables under 'project/' paths and read-only access to 'system/' paths.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/concepts/variables.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
namespace "dev" {
  policy       = "write"
  capabilities = ["alloc-node-exec"]

  variables {

    # full access to variables in all "project" paths
    path "project/*" {
      capabilities = ["write", "read", "destroy", "list"]
    }

    # read/list access within a "system/" path belonging to administrators
    path "system/*" {
      capabilities = ["read"]
    }
  }
}
```

