TITLE: Volume Interpolation in Nomad Job Specification
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates volume interpolation in a Nomad job specification. It shows how to use multiple volumes with multiple allocations using the 'per_alloc' field and HCL2 variables interpolation to expose information to the task's environment.
