TITLE: Downloading and Installing CNI Plugins for Nomad on Linux
DESCRIPTION: This shell script detects the system architecture, downloads the CNI plugins package (version 1.6.2), and extracts the binaries to the /opt/cni/bin directory. The script handles both amd64 and arm64 architectures automatically.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/partials/install/install-cni-plugins.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
export ARCH_CNI=$( [ $(uname -m) = aarch64 ] && echo arm64 || echo amd64)
export CNI_PLUGIN_VERSION=v1.6.2
curl -L -o cni-plugins.tgz "https://github.com/containernetworking/plugins/releases/download/${CNI_PLUGIN_VERSION}/cni-plugins-linux-${ARCH_CNI}-${CNI_PLUGIN_VERSION}".tgz && \
  sudo mkdir -p /opt/cni/bin && \
  sudo tar -C /opt/cni/bin -xzf cni-plugins.tgz
```

