TITLE: JWT Configuration Parameters
DESCRIPTION: Parameters specific to JWT authentication including validation keys, bound audiences, and timing configurations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/partials/api-docs/auth-method-params.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: markdown
