SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/hcl2/functions/collection/range.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: shell-session
CODE:
```
> range(3)
[
  0,
  1,
  2,
]

> range(1, 4)
[
  1,
  2,
  3,
]

> range(1, 8, 2)
[
  1,
  3,
  5,
  7,
]

> range(1, 4, 0.5)
[
  1,
  1.5,
  2,
  2.5,
  3,
  3.5,
]

> range(4, 1)
[
  4,
  3,
  2,
]

> range(10, 5, -2)
[
  10,
  8,
  6,
]
```

