TITLE: Configuring GCP Cloud KMS Keyring in Nomad Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure a GCP Cloud KMS keyring in the Nomad configuration file. It includes setting required parameters like credentials path, GCP project, region, key ring, and crypto key.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/configuration/keyring/gcpckms.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
keyring "gcpckms" {
  active = true
  name   = "example"

  credentials = "/etc/nomad.d/nomad-user-creds.json"
  project     = "nomad-project"
  region      = "global"
  key_ring    = "nomad-keyring"
  crypto_key  = "nomad-key"
}
```

