TITLE: Disabling Rescheduling in Nomad Job Specification
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to disable the rescheduling feature in a Nomad job by setting attempts to zero and unlimited to false. This prevents Nomad from automatically rescheduling failed allocations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/job-specification/reschedule.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
job "docs" {
  group "example" {
    reschedule {
      attempts  = 0
      unlimited = false
    }
  }
}
```

