TITLE: Configuring OIDC Client Assertion with Nomad Keyring for Keycloak
DESCRIPTION: JSON configuration for OIDC client assertion using Nomad's internal private key. This setup is for Keycloak and uses Nomad's jwks.json endpoint for key verification, providing enhanced security as the private key remains within Nomad.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/concepts/acl/auth-methods/oidc.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
