TITLE: Configuring Multiple Service Tags in Nomad HCL
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to configure multiple service blocks with the same name but different ports and tags. It allows for grouping services and querying specific protocols using tags.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad/blob/main/website/content/docs/networking/service-discovery.mdx#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
job "..." {
  # ...
  group "..." {
    network {
      port "http" {}
      port "grpc" {}
    }

    service {
      name = "my-app"
      port = "http"
      tags = ["http"]
      # ...
    }

    service {
      name = "my-app"
      port = "grpc"
      tags = ["grpc"]
      # ...
    }
  }
}
```

